summary: Reasons to be friends with a Swiftie
body:
Reasons to be friends with a Swiftie

  1. They are super loyal! (From loving Taylor through thick and thin)
  2. They are accepting! Swifties are part of an amazing and accepting community!
  3. They support successful women! (Taylor)
  4. They are really committed! They create posts blogs and edits of their queen and work really hard to provide support for Taylor!
  5. Last but not least… they have great taste in people! They love Taylor! Who is a beautiful, inspirational, kind, talented and smart woman! Enjoy being the fun of being friends with a Swiftie!

summary: I know I’m just a girl who is probably really insignificant but I love Taylor Swift so much and literally the impact she has...
